Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.21,0:13:46.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Protect Iceburg-{\i1}san{\fs15} {\r}!{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where did he go?!}Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where is he? Where{ is he}?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! Don't shoot a pistol! \NWe're inside, remember?}Idiot! Don't shoot your pistol in here!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's not good for Iceburg-{\i1}san{\fs15} {\r}!{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry about the commotion \Noutside the room.}I'm sorry about the commotion outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um{...}, what's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.81,0:14:23.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was told that Straw Hat Luffy \Nhas broken into this building.}I was told that Straw Hat Luffy \Nhas broken into the building.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa{...}, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whoa! So many of them!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He's going to Building {#2}Two! \NGo around from upstairs!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She is...}It's her!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kalifa-san, didn't a pirate come here?}Kalifa-{\i1}san{\i0}, did a pirate come this way?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't. More importantly, \Nchase after him more quietly.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-san still needs to rest quietly.}Iceburg-{\i1}san{\i0} {needs quiet to rest}is still recovering.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like the Straw Hat \Nhasn't reached this far yet.}{Looks like Straw Hat \Nhasn't reached this far yet.} Looks like Straw Hat \Nhasn't gotten this far yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's stand watch around here.}Let's stand watch here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,His target is definitely this room!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.30,0:15:29.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well...}Um, you wanted to see me{...}, right, pirate {lad}kid?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.91,0:15:33.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's right. Thanks for calling me in. That saved me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.69,0:15:38.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I doubt you came all the way here by yourself \Nto kill me in this commotion.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.19,0:15:40.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I came to hear the truth!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Last night, I saw Nico Robin with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,And{...} she is one of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Was it really Robin?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't say a word.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Your words no longer mean anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I called you in here...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,because I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.49,0:16:12.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let me see Nico Robin again now!
