Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.41,0:16:18.25,Captions-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,761)\fad(350,350)\blur0.6\bord0\fscx160\fscy160\fsp1\c&HE7E7E8&\4a&HFF&}Blue Station
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.54,0:16:18.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We're here! We're here! \NGrandma Kokoro! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Water Seven.{..} It's been a while.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.72,0:16:30.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Grandma! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.14,0:16:36.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wearing a mask is prohibited today \Nwhen you get on board the sea train.}Today, wearing a mask is prohibited{ today }\Nwhile boarding the sea train.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Please show me your ticket and your face.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is my own face! My own face!}This {\i1}is{\i0} my face!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm?}Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh! Kokoro-{\i1}san{\fs15} {\r}! Hello!{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.74,0:16:56.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes... We're after the Straw Hats \Nwho're the culprits} {in Iceburg-san's attempted assassination.}Oh, we're hunting the Straw Hats. Seems they're \Nresponsible for Iceburg-{\i1}san{\i0}'s attempted assassination.{Joined two lines - JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg's assassination? Hm?}Iceburg? Assassination? Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Ah...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,These people{...}?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.67,0:17:12.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again. Let me see Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's not possible.}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gunfire!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It came from the bedroom!{Slightly retimed this}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Iceburg-{\i1}san{\fs15} {\r}!{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Y-You're okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I bet on a silly hope\Nthat I might{ be able to} get closer to the truth.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capture{...} all the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey Luffy{...},
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wwere you able to talk\Nto}did you get a chance to talk to Iceburg-{\i1}san{\fs18} {\r by any chance}?{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He said he really saw Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can't be...! Why would Robin \Ndo something like that?}It can't be{...}! Why would Robin \Ndo something like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.70,Captions-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,694)\fad(400,0)\blur0.8\bord2.6\fscx165\fscy165\c&H1C1B1E&\3c&H1C1B1E&\1a&HFF&\t(355,400,\1a&H00&)}Main Street\NWater Seven
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.70,Captions-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,694)\fad(400,0)\blur0.8\bord0\fscx165\fscy165\c&HEBECEA&\4a&HFF&}Main Street\NWater Seven
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yow! }How's it going, Blueno?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.89,0:18:44.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Is it going super?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I think we're doing good.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.61,0:18:52.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, "I think"?! \NYou sure are an indecisive guy!}What do you mean, "I think"?! \NYou're such an indecisive guy!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give me the usual! Fill them up!}Give me the usual! Fill 'em up!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You got money?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just refill them! Cola!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that you run a bar with such a stingy notion}Why would you run your bar so greedily
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that you take money from your customers...!}as to take money from your customers?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We've got money.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've got a million belly left over from shopping.}We have a million belly left over.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've got that much money from yesterday?!}We've got that much money left from yesterday?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How shameful! How uncool!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.47,0:19:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that I didn't spend it all yesterday...!}I can't believe I didn't spend it all yesterday!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, give it to me!}Give it here!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.52,0:19:24.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yow! You guys! You're lucky!}{Yow! }You guys are lucky!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All your alcohol is on me!}All your drinks are on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.31,0:19:31.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Drink as much as you like!}Drink to your hearts' content!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! That's our Franky! You're generous!}Whoa! That's our Franky! So generous!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're the man! The face\Nof the Water Seven underworld! Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, there's more on the floor over there!}Hey, there's more over there!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.29,0:19:45.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Blueno! Where's my cola?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, already!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're doing well for yourself, Franky.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm}Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Old hag Kokoro! That was you?!}Kokoro, you old hag! That was you?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought it was a statue of a monster!}{I thought you were a statue of a monster!}I thought you were some sorta' {bestial}monster statue!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it okay to get a refill for my juice, Franky?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.52,0:20:10.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a bar. It's not a place for kids!}This is a bar. It's no place for kids!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're doing well, {right}aren't ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.07,0:20:15.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Okay, then. Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,All right! Juice!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.82,0:20:21.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm doing well, \Nbut I'm feeling gloomy. I feel terrible.}Sure, I'm doing well, \Nbut I'm in a bad mood. I feel terrible.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.95,0:20:26.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling terrible this week, \Nthanks to that damn pirate!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here's the refilled cola! Thanks for waiting!}{Here's your cola}All filled up! Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, took you long enough!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fuel! Fuel!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.34,0:20:40.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here it comes! Here it comes! Oh, yeah!}Here it comes. Here it comes. \NHere it comes!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.60,0:20:55.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've revived! That jerk! \NNext time I see him, I'll beat him up!}I'm re-energized! \NNext time I see that jerk, he's done for{I'll beat him up}!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,By the way, old hag, why are you here?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqua Laguna is coming.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.41,0:21:05.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that right? \NNo wonder the wind is strong.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Are you done getting your house ready?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.91,0:21:10.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Well, my house is gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I've got nothing that could sink, \Nso I have no worries.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.13,0:21:23.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I was going to have a drink with Iceburg, \Nbut I heard he got shot.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, {sounds like it}that's what I heard too.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They say it was the pirates' doing.}They're saying those pirates did it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Galley-La and the townspeople \Nare furious right now.}Galley-La and the townsfolk \Nare livid right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pirates' doing?}Pirates did it?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do you seriously think that's the case?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You sound like you know something.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't say whatever comes to mind, old hag.}Don't say whatever pops into your head, old hag.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.57,0:21:45.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg has been getting nagged all this time \Nby the World Government, right?}The World Government has been \Nnagging Iceburg for a long time.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.28,0:21:50.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then, what?\NAre you saying that official, Corgi, did it?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That tubby isn't an assassin type!}That tubby blob {isn't}ain't the assassin{ating} type!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.63,0:21:58.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No... Shadowy incidents are the work of CP9.}No{...}, {such things}covert ops are the work of CP9.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do you know about it, Blueno?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just heard some rumors.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.63,0:22:08.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... Common folk sure do like to believe \Nrumors of things like nonexistent organizations.}Cripes. {Plebs}The sheeple sure do swallow up \Nevery crazy tale about secret organizations.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How foolish... It does exist.}How foolish. It does exist.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.27,0:22:17.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But they never show themselves, \Nsince {their unit works secretly in the shadows}they're a secretive black-ops unit.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.20,0:22:26.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where's that confidence coming from? \NDo you know something?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.03,0:22:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard about it over there.}I heard about it from some guy.{Diverges from the Japanese, but captures the spirit of the line better in english}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.08,0:22:34.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's just a rumor, then! \NDon't mess with–
Dialogue: 5,0:22:34.92,0:22:38.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It always being a rumor is the scary part.}The scary thing is that it's {\i1}always{\i0} a rumor.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.13,0:22:42.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They eliminate people without anyone noticing.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.51,0:22:45.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If you meddle with them, you're dead meat.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.48,0:22:57.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thanks. The job we had to do yesterday went well.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.11,0:22:59.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Well done, Nico Robin.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That was a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.53,0:23:10.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although naturally you're now \Nbeing pursued by the whole town.}Naturally. Although, now you're\Nbeing pursued by the whole town.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:10.49,0:23:12.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:12.25,0:23:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But that's just temporary.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:15.00,0:23:18.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's important is... tonight.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We'll infiltrate Iceburg's residence one more time.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:22.26,0:23:27.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If worse comes to worst, \N{it's okay to eliminate}I don't mind eliminating all the evidence.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Among the disciples of this \NTom guy who originally had it,}Tom had it originally, and of his disciples,
